{"tid":2504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[感謝HKG+區] 多謝你地為我地iPhone做一切","createTime":"2016-11-25T21:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-25T22:06:32.000Z","uid":3646,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9de60e6eee14d861feddd5de910677bb39e7487e","tid":2504,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T21:26:10.000Z","msg":"致LIHKG Admin, 連尼住, 望遠:<br />\n<br />\n自從知道左iphone將會11/25之後無得用HKG+之後,<br />\n傷心左好耐,因為高登有好多令你同我難忘既事, 包括佔中<br />\n<br />\n我知道hkg+依個網站同你地完全無關係，亦都無代出被你地<br />\n<br />\n但好感激你地出手出力,一手一腳為我地iPhone user做到最好<br />\n<br />\n不管你地要去外國工作等,大家都對高登有感情,感謝你地 2 年來一直既支持, 呢個令我睇到香港人真情既一面<br />\n#連尼住<br />\n#望遠<br />\n#HKG+<br />\n我知你地無收獲,但有無限付出,不管你地幾多收費,我都無限支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望LIHKG將來會更好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母, 林早洩</span></span>"},{"pid":"e27d9f7fed5ce34342c47e5c8bc2bfe3752ce333","tid":2504,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T21:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccd496b949eb84416bf5e8e4b1b22e5c8191444","tid":2504,"uid":4372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T21:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124544b37e64c2c2985d594c18d00bac243935fa","tid":2504,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike